                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5803" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1475</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8526 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">传统商务酒店的蝶变之旅——开元森泊的前世今生</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Transformation of Traditional Business Hotel-The Past and Present Business Model of New Century Senbo</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">项国鹏，张微，肖迪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杭州开元森泊旅游投资有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商业模式；商业模式创新；商务酒店</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Business model; business model innovation; business hotel</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着旅游消费人群不断迭代，人们度假游与亲子游需求迅猛增加，旅游市场需求的变化正在深刻影响着旅游业（有删减）。在这种背景下，传统商务酒店唯有瞄准风口，不断创新，才能在日益激烈的竞争中站稳脚跟，持续发展。以传统酒店发家开元旅业集团，面对酒店行业的红海市场，不惜十年磨一剑，突破传统酒店局限，最终打造出一个集住宿、游乐、餐饮、商务为一体的“一站式休闲度假综合体”—开元森泊度假乐园（简称开元森泊）。2019年，开元森泊度假乐园在休闲度假市场崭露头角，在开业首年即实现了盈利，成为2019年江浙沪亲子游市场最强劲的黑马，在2020年疫情期间也表现突出，成为中国酒店业疫情后复苏的标杆企业，在业内引起了相当的关注。传统商务酒店在当前背景下如何顺应市场需求，谋求创新？开元森泊的案例具有很大的启发意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the continuous iteration of tourism consumer groups, people&#39;s demand for vacation travel and family travel increases rapidly, and the change of tourism market demand is profoundly affecting the tourism industry. In this context, the traditional business hotels only aiming at the outlet, continuous innovation, they can stand firm in the increasingly fierce competition and receive sustainable development. Based on traditional hotels, New Century Tourism Group, in the face of the Red Sea market of the hotel industry, has been sparing no effort for ten years to break through the limitations of traditional hotels and finally create a &quot;one-stop leisure resort complex&quot; -- New Century Senbo Holiday Park (New Century Senbo for short) integrating accommodation, entertainment, catering and business. In 2019, New Century Senbo Resort emerged in the leisure holiday market and achieved profitability in the first year of its opening, becoming the strongest dark horse in the parent-child travel market in Jiangsu, Zhejiang and Shanghai in 2019. It also performed well during the epidemic in 2020 and became a benchmark enterprise in the recovery of China&#39;s hotel industry after the epidemic, attracting considerable attention in the industry. How do traditional business hotels adapt to market demand and seek innovation under the current background? The case of New Century Senbo is of great enlightening significance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《旅游市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商业模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
                            </tr>
